snippet.title: Announcing: Dolan Kart TURBO - HUGE GAME UPDATE
snippet.description:
Play as PECAN in a new story mode - experience customisable karts/wheels/trails/components along with a new level and new ability: Sugar Rush! Download (Android/IOS) and start racing today for FREE!
Android ► https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chunkworks.dolankart&hl=en
Apple ► https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/dolan-kart/id1316860571

Join the DK discord community! ► https://discord.gg/PgVpHmz
Please remember to report bugs and issues by emailing support@chunk.works - we're happy to help!

NEW CONTENT OVERVIEW
---
New character: Pecan
New level: Pecan's Paradise
New ability: Sugar Rush
- Collect candy on the track to replenish hp with the new health bar system. The best ability for endless mode if you're aiming for a high score!
- 100+ missions in the new story mode
- Completely customisable karts
- New skins like Raven Melissa and Dark Knight Nixxiom
